strong>length</strong></a> is the metre.
1 metre is equal to 1.3123359580052 steps, or 0.00062137119223733 miles.
Note that rounding errors may occur, so always check the results.
Use this page to learn how to convert between steps and miles.
Type in your own numbers in the form to convert the units!
